name: Midnight Ice
description:
This beautifully embellished crop top is a very classy, yet daring piece. It is embellished with black sequins to form a leafy/floral print also with the leaf pattern stitched with silvery thread. It is a vintage item that I thrifted myself and has never been worn after purchase. It kind of reminds me of an Ice Skater's top, hence the title "Midnight Ice," for it being of a dark navy-black color. It is very form fitting and sets on the body just right. Cropped into a V-Shape form at the bottom, hits just past the belly button.

Brand: Papell Boutique "Evening"
Size: PS ( I'd say it's petite, small)
Material : 100% Silk , Lining 100% Polyester
*Never been worn after purchase

name: Home Bound Dress
description:
This dress gives off a western/earthy vibe. It has a pattern of little blue feathers and a cool background to match. It features "bat-wing," sleeves and have extra fabric attached to the waist to tie in the back to adjust to ones liking. Also a slight V-Neck neckline with scallop trim lace detailing surrounding the neck area as seen in the picture. As for color, it is a burnt orange color, a rich orange or more of a sienna. It is a size S and hits above the knee for the person of my height (5'1). It is a dress pre-owned(me being the owner), and only worn once. In great condition and will be great with a pair of brown knee-high boots or even some cute wedges for the summer.

Brand : Everly
Size: Small (fits loosely)
*Hits above the knee on myself being 5'1"
**Worn once, like-new
